@NODE "disk mix" "disk mix"
@TOC "MAIN"


      Open 8-track-stereo-mixer window in the menu window. Select 
      within the area MIXING TO DISK the DISK-button. Input in the request
      window a name for a new MTRS project and press the recording button. 
      All tracks will be mixed and saved on disk. If the stereo-mode is active, 
      will be created a stereo project (track 1+2), otherwise a mono project
      (track 1).
@ENDNODE

@NODE "errors" "errors"
@TOC "MAIN"


     Error description 
     -----------------  

     MTRS informs you by means of a Requesters about occurred Error.
     Here a short description: 

     Messages                        | possible causes
     ----------------------------------------------------------------- 
     DOS:
     Read errors                     | - file defectively 
                                     | - reading interrupted 
                                     | - multitasking switched off
     ----------------------------------------------------------------- 
     DOS:
     Incorrect file                  | - file defectively 
     ----------------------------------------------------------------- 
     DOS:
     Errors with write               | - file defectively 
                                     | - incorrect storage medium
                                     | - incorrect formatting 
                                     | - multitasking switched off
     ----------------------------------------------------------------- 
     DOS:
     File is not to open             | - file does not exist 
                                     | - incorrect path or file on gift
     ------------------------------------------------------------------ 
     EXEC:
     Graphics.library V36 not found  | - old Kickstart
     ------------------------------------------------------------------ 
     EXEC:
     Gadtools.library V36 not found  | - old Kickstart
     ------------------------------------------------------------------ 
     EXEC:
     Asl.library not found           | - old Kickstart
     ------------------------------------------------------------------ 
     EXEC:
     Diskfont.library not found      | - Diskfont.library is 
                                     |   not in the LIBS directory 
     ------------------------------------------------------------------ 
     EXEC: 
     No more fast memory !           | - Memory occupies by other programs
                                     | - computer possesses too few 
                                     |   fast memory
     ------------------------------------------------------------------ 
     EXEC:
     No more chip memory !           | - Memory occupies by other programs
                                     | - computer possesses too few 
                                     |   chip memory
     ------------------------------------------------------------------
     INTUITION: 
     Screen not too open             | - no memory (chip RAM) 
                                     | - too many bit planes (colours)
     ------------------------------------------------------------------
     INTUITION: 
     Error VisualInfo                | - ????
     ------------------------------------------------------------------
     INTUITION: 
     Error Gadgets                   | - no memory (structures 
                                     |   could not be created)
     ------------------------------------------------------------------
     INTUITION: 
     Can't open window               | - no memory (chip RAM) 
                                     | - window to big for screen
     ------------------------------------------------------------------ 
     MTRS: 
     No MTRS file                    | - unknown file
     ------------------------------------------------------------------ 
     MTRS:
     Unknown MTRS version            | - new project version + old 
                                     |   program version
     ------------------------------------------------------------------ 
     MTRS: 
     No original file                | - project file was changed 
                                     |   unauthorized 
     ------------------------------------------------------------------ 
     MTRS:
     Computer or disk is too         | - performance of the processor 
     slow for                        |   or HD is too small 
     sample frequency                |
     ------------------------------------------------------------------ 
     MTRS:
     MTRS-Font6 not found            | - MTRS-Font6 is does not find 
                                     |   in the Font directory
     ------------------------------------------------------------------ 
     MTRS:
     MTRS-Font13 not found           | - MTRS-Font13 is does not find 
                                     |   in the Font directory
     ------------------------------------------------------------------ 
     MTRS:
     >HDR:< is not mount             | - starting from MTRS V1.6 not       
                                     |   necessarily
     ------------------------------------------------------------------ 
     MTRS:
     Player V1.4 not found           | - Player program is not 
                                     |   in the MTRS directory
     ------------------------------------------------------------------ 
     MTRS:
     Audio channels are not          | - audio channels became 
     available !                     |   other programm occupies 
                                     | - audio channels were released by MTRS 
                                     |   (menu settings/audio channels)
     ------------------------------------------------------------------ 
     MTRS:
     Error unknown                   | -???? (audio device)
     ------------------------------------------------------------------ 
     MTRS:
     MTRS already is running         | - MTRS can't starts do several times 
                                     |   
     ------------------------------------------------------------------ 
     MTRS:
     File path is too long           | - path length (path name[s]+file name) 
                                     |   exceeds reserved to memory 
                                     |   (error might not occur actually)
     ------------------------------------------------------------------ 
     MTRS:
     File already exists             | - everything said!
     ------------------------------------------------------------------ 
     MTRS:
     Accesses to disk is not         | - MTRS plays sample files directly of 
     possible in play mode           |   disk, other accesses is not
     Abort please playback and       |   possible 
     repeat process                  |
     ------------------------------------------------------------------ 
     TOOLBOX:
     Incorrect INFO file             | - INF file defectively or was 
                                     |   stored incompletely 
     ------------------------------------------------------------------ 
     TOOLBOX:
     Could not delete empty          | - file in use
     INFO file                       |
     ------------------------------------------------------------------ 
     MTRS:
     Could not save preferences      | - I/O-error or no memory
     ------------------------------------------------------------------ 
     MTRS:
     Could not load preferences      | - missing MTRS.prefs in the  
                                     |   directory S: 
                                     | - File defectively
     ------------------------------------------------------------------ 
     MTRS:
     Audio tracks are not available  | - empty project 
     ------------------------------------------------------------------ 
@ENDNODE

@NODE "main window functions" "functions"
@TOC "MAIN"


    Main window
    ------------------------------------------------------------------ 
 
    STOP           - abort playback 
    START          - start playback at position zero  
    PLAY           - start playback at current position  
    REW            - degrades position 
    FFW            - increases position 
    REC            - start recording process 
    MODE 1 - 4     - selects record mode
    RECORD > >     - selects record track 
    PLAY 1 - 3 > > - selects playback track 
    MIC ON/OFF     - Sampler micro switches off on 
    CHAN L/R       - selects Sampler channel  
    PERIOD         - set sample cycle 
    FREQUENCE      - set sample frequency 
    MONITOR        - starts Sampler monitor s
    REC_VOL        - adjust the monitoring volume  
    PLAY_VOL       - adjust the playback volume in mode 2/4 
    DMA/PROCESSOR  - display DMA or processor playback 
    PLAY 2 - 8     - select the playback routine 
    HQ ON/OFF      - multitasking on/off 
    FILTER ON/OFF  - hardware low-pass filter on/off 
    SYS INFO       - hardware configuration and max. playback frequency 
    CHANNEL 1-8    - channels 1-8 switch on/off 
    OPEN           - open MTRS project 
    SAVE           - saves adjustments 
    SONGNAME       - contain project name
@ENDNODE

@NODE "mixer window functions" "functions"
@TOC "MAIN"


      Mixer window
      ------------------------------------------------------------------ 

      PANORAMA 1-8    - adjust the position of the track (stereo) 
      VOLUME   1-8    - sets the volume for each track 
      MIXVOL %        - sets the mixing volume 
      STEREO          - checkmarks = stereo / no checkmark = mono 
      TEST            - checkmarks = playback test actively 
      FREQ/2          - checkmarks = Resample actively 
      MIXING TO DISK  - starts disk-mix 
      MASTER L-R      - sets final volume for left and right channel 
@ENDNODE

@node "functions AHImix" "functions AHImix" 
@toc " MAIN "


      AHI mixer 
      ------------------------------------------------------------------

      PANORAMA 1-8    - adjust the position of the track (stereo) 
                        (not all AHI modes) 
      VOLUME   1-8    - sets the volume for each track 
      CHAN     1-8    - channel on/off switches 
      SURR     1-8    - channel for surround codes 
                        (not all AHI modes) 
      EFF      1-8    - yet not supported


      AHI-DSP 
      ------------------------------------------------------------------

      DELAY           - adjust the delay for echo 
                        (0=Echo off; val=1/10 seconds.)  
      FEED            - number of echo  0=Delay 
      MIX 	          - the mixing ratio signal/effect 
      CROSS           - cross echo - only in the stereo mode meaningfully

      MASTER          - the final volume for all channels 
                        (not all AHI Modes) 
      BOOST           - mixvolume 
      BUFFER          - sets size of the disk memory for playback



@endnode


@NODE "toolbox window functions" "functions"
@TOC "MAIN"


       Toolbox window
       ------------------------------------------------------------------ 

       SONG END            - final position in bytes 
       SONG TIME           - play time in hours, minutes, seconds
       MEM 1-4             - sets stored positions 
       SET 1-4             - stores positions 
       START               - the beginning of the area which can be exported 
       END                 - the end of the area which can be exported 
       SET (START)         - stores starting position 
       SET (END)           - stores final position 
       Text field (START)  - starting position can be input directly 
       Text field (END)    - final position can be input directly 
       SAMPLE LEN          - length of the area in bytes, which can be exported 
       TRACK LEN           - length of the current track in bytes 
       SELECT              - selects current track 
       EXPORT              - starts the export and conversion process 
       IMPORT              - starts the import process
@ENDNODE

@NODE "installation" "installation"
@TOC "MAIN"


      The installation of MTRS is very simple. Click on Install-MTRS icon.
@ENDNODE

@NODE "short instruction" "short instruction"
@TOC "MAIN"


      Read @{"installation" LINK "installation"} before. 

      Install your Sampler. 
      Create sufficiently storage space on your disk. 
      Start MTRS now. 
      Input a name for your MTRS project.
      Leave please frequency to the adjusted value. 
      Select record-mode1 in the main window and set RECORDS to TRACK 1. 
      Start the @{"Sampler monitor" LINK "monitor"}.
      Adjust your sampler-signal with hearing or graphic display.
      Thus will be avoided over-regulations. 
      Close the window with the left mouse button. 
      Click on REC. 
      Close the request window with "NO". 
      MTRS waits now for the beginning of recording. 
      Press the left mouse button. 
      The recording begins.
      The right mouse stop the recording.

      Select record-mode 2 and set RECORD to TRACK 2. 
      PLAY 1 will be set automatically to TRACK 1. 
      Restart the recording process. 
      While the second recording is runs (TRACK 2), 
      the first track (TRACK 1) is replays (FULL DUPLEX).
@ENDNODE

@NODE "monitor" "sampler monitor"
@TOC "MAIN"


     The Samplermonitor plots sound signals. 
     (left channel = left field; right channel = right field) 
     The sampler signal will be scaned with 44,1 khz in stereo. The diagram 
     will be drawn in real time. Adjust your sampler-signal with hearing or
     graphic display. Thus will be avoided over-regulations. The right mouse 
     button frozen the display. The left mouse button close the window.
@ENDNODE

